    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "In short, I'd like to have you continue to keep in contact",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "with me, and relay to me anything further you learn.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "In turn, I'll give you the whole story, which I'm just about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "ready to break (not in the newspapers). And if it was as",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "dangerous as you seem to suspect, I'm afraid I'd have been",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "a corpse long ago!",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "But, and this is all you need remember, those disks are not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "red corpuscles in your eyeball, and they are not something",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "we can forget about with an ostrich in the sand attitude.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "We've got to solve them, public hysteria or no. As for that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "hysteria, if laughing is hysteria, that's all the hysteria",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "I've noticed!",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "You know your business, and you handled it like a major.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "But I'm hoping you do the easy part now and get that report",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "on paper.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
